325
00:22:21,470 --> 00:22:25,030
<i>MÍNOVÉ POLE
NEVSTUPOVAŤ!!!</i>

326
00:22:25,030 --> 00:22:27,350
Hotovo. Poďme.

327
00:22:27,350 --> 00:22:29,180
Počkajte.

328
00:22:36,010 --> 00:22:39,650
Nie každý vie po anglicky.

329
00:22:46,690 --> 00:22:48,930
Nesťažujem sa,

330
00:22:48,930 --> 00:22:52,430
